閉；中心內的貝夫人普通科門診診所夜間門診服務暫停。診所已聯絡相關病人作相應安排。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同大陸一撚樣 連睇醫生都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n北京國慶進入臨戰狀態 不能生病，住院病人只可出不可進 斷煤氣禁止家中煮食<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589302\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589302</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"今晚港島宵禁呀？"},{"pid":"334af404a76a1b6404140f0e0fc21c5b2e58bbde","tid":1595652,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}